00:24:09,300 --> 00:24:13,300
Anyway, he realized that what Faraday and others had been discovering

279
00:24:13,300 --> 00:24:17,300
could be written in the language of calculus,

280
00:24:17,300 --> 00:24:20,300
that there were certain laws about electricity and magnetism,

281
00:24:20,300 --> 00:24:26,300
specifically how changing an electric field could produce magnetic effects

282
00:24:26,300 --> 00:24:30,300
and changing electric fields, or did I say that first?

