00:27:27,300 --> 00:27:34,300
He has this prediction from calculus and these known physical laws that light can move as an electromagnetic wave,

323
00:27:34,300 --> 00:27:36,300
and it doesn't have to just be light.

324
00:27:36,300 --> 00:27:40,300
There can be other kinds of non-visible forms of electromagnetic waves.

